HEADWORD: Two-ranked
<hw>Two"-ranked`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Alternately disposed on exactly opposite sides of the stem so as to
from two ranks; distichous.</def>⟦br⟧
